This code requires the following prerequisites to run:
1. Pycluster module for python
2. Networkx module for python
3. igraph library for python
4. matplotlib to observe the graphical representation of graphs   
5. Two dataset files named "twittercrawl.dot" and "twitter.gml" which is also present in the repository and can also be downloaded from the following link(http://wiki.gephi.org/index.php/Datasets) (PS: You can only download the ".dot" file from the link but not the "dot" file, but you can use the file I provide or convert it yourself using Gephi)



